Package spx.packets

Provides definitions for SPx packets.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AlertLogicFlags
    Defines bit flags for the optional fields in the AlertLogic report.
    BlobFlags
    Defines bit flags for the blob flags field in the Plot report.
    EnhancedFlags
    Defines bit flags for the optional fields in the Plot report.
    IFFConfFlags
    Defines bit flags for the IFF confidence flags fields in the Secondary report.
    IFFExtFlags
    Defines bit flags for the IFF extended flags fields in the Secondary and Plot reports.
    IFFFlags
    Defines bit flags for the IFF flags fields in the Secondary and Plot reports.
    TrackerStatusFlags
    Defines bit flags for the optional fields in the TrackerStatus report.
    Type
    Define the packetType values for SPxPacketHeaderB headers.

Package spx.packets Description

Provides definitions for SPx packets. (e.g. for recording files or network transmission etc.)
